Interface IManyItemQueryModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IItemQueryModel, IManyQueryModel, IQueryModel
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IBaseBuildDefinitionQueryModel.IManyBuildDefinitionQueryModel, IBaseBuildEngineQueryModel.IManyBuildEngineQueryModel, IBaseBuildFolderEntryQueryModel.IManyBuildFolderEntryQueryModel, IBaseBuildResultQueryModel.IManyBuildResultQueryModel, IBaseCoreDescriptorQueryModel.IManyCoreDescriptorQueryModel, IBaseFolderDescriptorQueryModel.IManyFolderDescriptorQueryModel, IBaseReportDescriptorQueryModel.IManyReportDescriptorQueryModel, IBaseReportQueryDescriptorQueryModel.IManyReportQueryDescriptorQueryModel, IBaseSharableDescriptorQueryModel.IManySharableDescriptorQueryModel, IBaseStorageNodeQueryModel.IManyStorageNodeQueryModel

    public interface IManyItemQueryModel
extends IManyQueryModel, IItemQueryModel
    Represents the query model for a many valued reference to items. Instances of this interface can be acquired by starting at a query model root and navigating to a many valued reference to an item type.
    Since:
    0.5
